		<p>
			Set default wallpapers for dark and light mode!
		</p>
		<p>
			Features:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Persistent mode (keep the app running in the background)</li>
			<li>Run at startup (run in the background automatically when the session starts)</li>
		</ul>
	</description>
